WEBVTT

00:03.069 --> 00:05.336
¶ Boy, the way
Glenn Miller played ¶

00:05.404 --> 00:09.040
¶ songs that made
the hit parade ¶

00:09.108 --> 00:12.644
¶ guys like us
we had it made ¶

00:12.712 --> 00:16.982
[ together ]
¶ those were the days ¶

00:17.049 --> 00:21.219
<i>¶ and you knew</i>
<i> </i> <i>where you were then ¶</i>

00:21.286 --> 00:24.956
[ Archie ]
¶ girls were girls
and men were men ¶

00:25.024 --> 00:26.891
[ Archie, Edith ]
¶ mister, we could use a man ¶

00:26.959 --> 00:32.229
¶ like Herbert hoover again ¶

00:32.296 --> 00:35.266
[ Archie ]
¶ didn't need no welfare state ¶

00:35.334 --> 00:38.770
[ Edith ]
¶ everybody pulled his weight ¶

00:38.838 --> 00:42.674
[ Archie, Edith ]
¶ gee, our old lasalle
ran great ¶

00:42.742 --> 00:48.246
¶ those were the days ¶

